{"tid":847764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【拉手掣呀喂】屯公出九龍14車串燒 至少11人傷","createTime":"2018-10-04T11:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T05:58:58.000Z","uid":7441,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"893685641ea1d21b7e7e49942e02f2e600c47556","tid":847764,"uid":7441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:54:17.000Z","msg":"唔識揸車真係咪害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傍晚6時許，屯門公路出九龍方向近汀九交匯處發生14車相撞意外，意外中至少11人受傷。現場消息指，最前方一輛的士與3輛私家車發生相撞，3人受傷，其後駛至的8輛私家車及1輛的士懷疑收掣不及，同時相撞，再有8人受傷。受事故影響，上址交通嚴重擠塞，龍尾塞至嘉龍村，屯門公路往九龍方向近豪景花園的部份行車線現已封閉，運輸署呼籲駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181004&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58756762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181004%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58756762&d=fph60a7mJUwJE%2BnUXaOkiTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b6ecd2fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181004%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58756762&h=648f872d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181004&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58756762</a>"},{"pid":"41caeff17fb0b51446e4aca47d248b2218f9cb28","tid":847764,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f44857070daf115988ed6294be82b432d525d1c","tid":847764,"uid":7441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:08:38.000Z","msg":"塞到煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d597761bb4d1ca14b478ce242b937c18a78ea2b8","tid":847764,"uid":184100,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/202716_99fc7d445bb5988db70f4a1be0c22490.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb